{"tid":406820,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"火影港台譯名邊個好啲","createTime":"2017-09-20T03:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T13:00:56.000Z","uid":93443,"like":4,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"137e80f0d473f6bc46f0b571448f516471b48094","tid":406820,"uid":93443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:16:38.000Z","msg":"我知道睇開漫畫嘅人都習慣用台譯，但係某啲譯名我又覺得港譯好啲。<br />\n好似內輪同宇智波咁，宇智波好明顯係音譯，從宇智波三個字係睇唔到意思，而內輪至起碼會令你聯想到寫輪眼，大部份日本姓氏都係可以有意思嘅例如速水，田中，你可以直接知道姓氏嘅意思，所以我覺得意譯嘅港名比起音譯嘅台名更好。<br />\n另外仲有旗木卡卡西同畑鹿驚，佢個名就係稻田稻草人，所以畑呢個字更能保持意思，大家又覺得點呢?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：睇台譯漫畫咁耐，點都唔可以轉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁港譯又真係好啲喎"},{"pid":"e7a3174688d4ecfe907ef905639488fb2a77173b","tid":406820,"uid":86587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:19:20.000Z","msg":"日向螺旋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b345a289b69d4ecbeb9be4a6cb717ee572c8a48","tid":406820,"uid":40867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:23:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日向螺旋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n漩渦？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff868cccaef288bb8d896dec0278172a8a0e9bd8","tid":406820,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:55:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2927b9f01f12845e8a2c641c0d9b7936bab3e5cc","tid":406820,"uid":82404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:57:39.000Z","msg":"邊個好聽用邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1a28499a4e11d0d131731580e3289b29dc0f9f","tid":406820,"uid":87515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T06:27:58.000Z","msg":"叫慣卡卡西<br />\n佐助成日聽人讀[左助]，平時自己叫[助助]，硬係覺得左助好唔順口"},{"